                <head>No. 206<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Agreement between the United States and Iraq providing for United States military
                    assistance to Iraq, was effected on April 21, 1954, by an exchange of notes in
                    Baghdad. For texts, see <hi rend="italic">United States Treaties and Other
                        International Agreements</hi> (<gloss target="#t_UST1">UST</gloss>), volume
                    5 (pt. 3), page 2497. The agreement entered into force immediately. For text of
                    the Department of State press release on the agreement issued April 26, see
                    Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, May 17, 1954, page 772.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
